data.description: Welcome Home! Seller to add new HVAC with a FULL PRICE OFFER! This is beautiful 4 Bedroom 2 bathroom home on .67 acres. This home has been renovated with upgrades to almost every room. Most rooms have a mounted television that stays. This home also boasts numerous updates throughout. With a split floor plan, tile and luxury vinyl floors, updated windows and doors you can see the love and care put into this home. The open concept with formal dining room, eat-in kitchen with high bar . The recently remodeled eat-in kitchen with high bar is loaded with beautiful cabinets, granite countertops and tile backsplash. All kitchen appliances are Newer and will convey with home. Both bathrooms have been Remodeled with granite tops, tiled floors and showers. Home security system conveys. All furniture with the exception of leather furniture and great room television are negotiable. The Exterior Offers: Low Maintenance Brick and Vinyl Siding, lush landscaping, sprinkler system, large driveway, and large privacy fenced backyard. Home is loacated close to I-10 for easy commute anywhere. Shopping and dining are only minutes away, as well as the beautiful Emerald Coast beaches. COME HOME AND EXPERIENCE SERENITY with no HOA! Buyer/buyer's agent to verify any and all information pertinent to the purchase of this property.
